article.story: CLARKSVILLE, Tenn. -- — Jordan Lathon had 21 points in Morehead State's 61-50 win against Austin Peay on Wednesday night. Lathon also had 12 rebounds for the Eagles (5-3). Riley Minix scored 17 points and added nine rebounds. Kalil Thomas shot 4 for 9, including 3 for 7 from beyond the arc to finish with 13 points, while adding six rebounds. Demarcus Sharp finished with 20 points, four assists and two steals for the Governors (3-5). Ja'Monta Black added nine points for Austin Peay. Dezi Jones also put up seven points and four steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
